#: maxframe.learn.metrics._classification.recall_score:84 of
msgid ""
"When ``true positive + false negative == 0``, recall returns 0 and raises"
" ``UndefinedMetricWarning``. This behavior can be modified with "
"``zero_division``."
msgstr ""
"当 ``true positive + false negative == 0`` 时，召回率返回 0 并引发 ``"
"UndefinedMetricWarning``。此行为可以通过 ``zero_division`` 参数进行修改。"

